			<div id="comment_title"><a href='http://gatheringinlight.com/2007/09/28/dress-down-friday-one-words/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Dress Down Friday | One Words</a> on <a href="#comment-1493" title="">September 28th, 2007 at 10:46 am</a> 						</div>
			

